### Create a new lesson
POST http://localhost:5000/api/lessons HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Math 101",
  "description": "Introduction to basic algebra",
  "teacher": "John Doe",
  "date": "2025-02-18"
}

###

### Get all lessons
GET http://localhost:5000/api/lessons HTTP/1.1

###

### Get a specific lesson by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/lessons/60d5f83d8d4e2c2a088f1d35 HTTP/1.1

###

### Update a lesson by ID
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/lessons/60d5f83d8d4e2c2a088f1d35 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Math 101 - Updated",
  "description": "Introduction to algebra and geometry",
  "teacher": "John Doe",
  "date": "2025-02-18"
}

###

### Delete a lesson by ID
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/lessons/60d5f83d8d4e2c2a088f1d35 HTTP/1.1
